Package: riskr
Version: 1.0
Title: Functions to Facilitate the Evaluation, Monitoring and Modeling process
Description: The riskr package facilitate credit scoring tasks
    such as measure the scores/models performance,
    the scoring modelling process, visualize relationships between variables.
    Also there are functions to compute usual values in the credit scoring
    like PSI, WOE, IV, KS, AUCROC, among others.
Author: Joshua Kunst <jbkunst@gmail.com>
